data.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom home sitting on 2.55 acres of land, providing plenty of space for various activities. Electrical system upgraded in 2022. Remodeled kitchen featuring a double oven, with all kitchen appliances included. All 4 bedrooms are generously sized. The large living room has a cozy fireplace. Home is eligible for 100% financing (no down payment) USDA loan and will also go FHA.  Call your agent today to schedule a showing.
